<title>SOUTH AFRICA: Minaco year pre-excep share rises.</title>
<headline>Minaco year pre-excep share rises.</headline>
<dateline>JOHANNESBURG 1997-04-10</dateline>
<text>
<p>Year ended Dec 31</p>
<p>			(million rand unless stated)</p>
<p>    Shr, attrib (cts)     3.0 loss    vs 32.9 loss</p>
<p>    Pre-excep shr (cts)   0.8 profit  vs 10.0 loss</p>
<p>    Attrib income	   2.4 loss    vs 14.1 loss</p>
<p>    Operating profit	4.5	   vs 0.4</p>
<p>    Finance charges	 3.9	   vs 4.7</p>
<p>    Net tax profit	  0.6 profit  vs 4.3 loss</p>
<p>    Turnover		  58.1	  vs 50.7</p>
<p>Full name: Minaco Granite &amp; Marble Ltd</p>
<p>    Exceptional items     3.0	   vs 9.8</p>
<p>NOTE - The firm said recent rains had a marked effect on current production, but a new railway siding has helped to maintain a regular export flow.</p>
<p>-- Johannesburg newsroom +27 11 482 1003</p>
